OL,3,CMan arrested after large fire destroys
OL,4,Chistoric mill in Staffordshire
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after a large
OL,7,Ffire destroyed a historic mill in
OL,8,FStaffordshire, as nearby homes were
OL,9,Fevacuated.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to The
OL,12,FBig Mill in Mill Street, Leek, at
OL,13,F9:35pm on Friday night.
OL,15,FThe blaze at the Grade II listed
OL,16,Fbuilding could be seen from miles away
OL,17,Fas people were advised to stay away
OL,18,Ffrom the area and keep their windows
OL,19,Fand doors closed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
