OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774969867
OL,3,CMan arrested after large fire destroys
OL,4,Chistoric mill in Staffordshire
OL,6,FStaffordshire Fire and Rescue said
OL,7,Fthey had six crews and an aerial
OL,8,Fladder platform at the scene of a
OL,9,Flarge fire.
OL,11,FStaffordshire Police said officers put
OL,12,Fvarious road closures in place within
OL,13,Fthe cordon and supported residents who
OL,14,Fhad been evacuated from their homes as
OL,15,Fa precaution.
OL,17,FAn 18-year-old man, from Leek, has
OL,18,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of arson
OL,19,Fwith recklessness as to whether life
OL,20,Fwas endangered. He remains in custody.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
