OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774969867
OL,3,CMan arrested after large fire destroys
OL,4,Chistoric mill in Staffordshire
OL,6,FThe A523 Mill Street and the
OL,7,Fneighbouring Bellevue remain closed
OL,8,Fthis morning.
OL,10,FA council report last year revealed
OL,11,Fthat the Grade-II listed six-storey
OL,12,FBig Mill remained unoccupied. It has
OL,13,Fplanning permission for 34 flats.
OL,15,FStaffordshire Moorlands MP Dame Karen
OL,16,FBradley wrote on social media: "I was
OL,17,Fso sad to see the terrible fire at the
OL,18,FBig Mill in Leek last night.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
